  "detailed_description": "Amber Time is a game that simulates life. You can experience life in supermarkets, restaurants, giant companies, etc<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTired of the luxurious life in the city, we can go to the fields to grow vegetables, raise pigs, etc<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou like all kinds of fragrant cars and beauties of the rich. You can invest in stocks and industries. Money in the bank is also making money. If you have more money, please call some bodyguards to protect you<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe map is very big. Drive your RV to explore the wild and dig the treasure house of nature<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you like the sea, you can take your yacht to the south sea for treasure hunting and sightseeing<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThose who like to fight with police and bandits can prepare guns and ammunition and open up freely. What kind of tanks and armour do they really have<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAmber world, let's feel the desire together! RPG with free role",
